- Also Owns 13 ski properties.

b"$EPR 

- Successfully restructured some of it's AMC leases, lowered near term costs for the tenant but extends the terms of the leases
- Topgolf 11-12% of their revenues and business is booming
- Movie theaters represent 45% of their revs, majority coming from $AMC and Regal"

b'$EPR EXPERIENCE REIT.

- $1B cash
- 6B of assets
- 45% revenues derived from movie theaters (largest AMC + Regal)
- Collected 41% contractual rent in Q3
- Q3 Cash flow -4M, but w 985M cash, rent collection expected to rise significantly
- No scheduled debt maturities til 2022'
